<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Meri Janakpur Yatra</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f9; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; padding: 20px; }
        header { background: #ff5722; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 10px; }
        .container { max-width: 800px; margin: 20px auto; background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        h2 { color: #ff5722; border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 10px; }
        .info-box { background: #fff3e0; padding: 15px; border-left: 5px solid #ff9800; margin: 15px 0; }
        footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 0.9em; color: #777; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>Jai Shree Ram! Janakpur Yatra</h1>
    <p>Aaj ki Tarikh: 26 March, 2026</p>
</header>

<div class="container">
    <h2>Janakpur Dham ki Jankari</h2>
    <p>Janakpur, jise Janakpurdham bhi kaha jata hai, Nepal ka ek mukhya dharmik kendra hai. Yeh Mata Sita ka janm sthal aur Raja Janak ki rajdhani mani jati hai.</p>

    <div class="info-box">
        <strong>Mukhya Akarshan:</strong>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Janaki Mandir:</strong> Yeh mandir Mughal aur Hindu shaili ka ek adbhut namuna hai.</li>
            <li><strong>Vivah Mandap:</strong> Maana jata hai ki yahi Bhagwan Ram aur Mata Sita ka vivah hua tha.</li>
            <li><strong>Pavitra Kund:</strong> Yahan Dhanush Sagar aur Ganga Sagar jaise kai pavitra talab hain.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <h2>Aaj ka Plan</h2>
    <p>Aaj hum Janakpur ki pawan dharti par darshan karenge aur vahan ki sanskriti ka anubhav lenge.</p>
</div>

<footer>
    <p>Banaya gaya hai Susheelcoder ke liye | Shubh Yatra!</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
